  "data": {
    "title": "Nutshell CRM Tips: Best Ways to Close More B2B Deals",
    "excerpt": "Discover the best ways to use Nutshell CRM for your B2B sales team. Pipeline tips, automation tricks, and honest features breakdown inside.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/nutshell-crm-tips.jpg",
        "alt": "Nutshell CRM Tips: Best Ways to Close More B2B Deals",
        "filename": "nutshell-crm-tips.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your sales team has ever struggled with a CRM that felt like piloting a spaceship just to log a call, Nutshell CRM is the breath of fresh air you've been waiting for. Built specifically for B2B teams who value simplicity without sacrificing power, Nutshell strips away the bloat and gives you exactly what you need to manage leads, automate follow-ups, and close deals faster.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've spent real time inside Nutshell, and in this guide I'm sharing the best ways to use it, the tips that actually move the needle, and why thousands of companies across 50 countries trust it with their pipeline. Let's dig in.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why Nutshell CRM Feels Different From Everything Else",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Most CRMs fall into two camps: too simple to be useful, or so complex that your team avoids logging in. Nutshell sits in a sweet spot that very few tools manage to hit.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-nutshell-crm"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The moment you create an account, you notice the difference. There's no 45-minute onboarding video. No \"consulting packages\" required just to set up a pipeline. You sign up, import your contacts, and you're genuinely selling within the hour. That speed-to-value is something ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I break down step by step in this Nutshell tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What makes it stick, though, is the depth underneath that simplicity. Customizable pipelines let you mirror your actual sales process—not a generic template someone else designed. Email sequences run on autopilot so your reps never forget a follow-up. Reporting dashboards show real revenue forecasts, not vanity metrics.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell has earned recognition as a leader in G2's reports, and the reviews on Gartner Peer Insights consistently highlight one theme: teams that adopt Nutshell actually *use* it. That alone puts it ahead of half the market.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.nutshell.com/ssuchcfp1lga"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your current CRM feels like homework, give Nutshell a try free for 14 days",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". No credit card required, and you'll know within a week whether it fits.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
