        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Best Ways to Use Nutshell CRM: 7 Tips That Work",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Build Your Pipeline Around Your Real Process",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Don't just use the default stages. Sit with your team and map out every meaningful step a deal goes through—from first touch to signed contract. Then recreate that inside Nutshell.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I recommend keeping it between 5 and 8 stages. Enough granularity to spot bottlenecks, few enough that reps don't skip stages out of laziness. You can drag deals between stages with a click, and the visual pipeline view makes it immediately obvious where revenue is stuck.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Set Up Email Sequences for Every Common Scenario",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell's email sequences are one of its strongest features, and most teams underuse them. Create sequences for:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New inbound leads (3-5 emails over two weeks)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Post-demo follow-ups",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Re-engagement for cold prospects",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Onboarding drip for new customers",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Each step can be personalized with merge fields, and you control the timing precisely. The result: consistent outreach without anyone manually copying and pasting templates.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/nutshell-crm-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For a closer look at ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "all the features packed into Nutshell's latest releases",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", check our detailed breakdown.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Use Automations to Eliminate Busywork",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell's automation engine handles the tedious stuff so your reps focus on conversations. A few automations I recommend setting up on day one:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Auto-assign new leads to reps based on territory or round-robin",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Move deals to \"Lost\" if no activity in 30 days",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Trigger a task when a deal moves to a specific stage",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Send internal Slack notifications when a high-value deal updates",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "These aren't hypothetical—they take minutes to configure and save hours every week.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Log Everything (and Make It a Team Habit)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A CRM is only as good as the data inside it. Nutshell makes logging painless: it syncs with your email and calendar automatically, capturing interactions without anyone lifting a finger. But encourage your team to add notes after calls, tag key stakeholders, and update deal values religiously.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The payoff comes in reporting. When the data is rich, Nutshell's forecasts become genuinely useful for planning.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. Customize Your Dashboard for What You Actually Care About",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell lets you build custom dashboards with the metrics that matter to your role. A sales manager might track pipeline value by rep and win rate. A rep might watch their upcoming tasks and sequence performance. An exec wants quarterly revenue forecasts and new lead volume.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Don't settle for the default view. Spend 15 minutes building dashboards for each role on your team.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "6. Integrate Your Stack",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-apollo-io"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell connects with the tools B2B teams already use: Google Workspace, Microsoft 365, Slack, Zapier, and dozens more. If you're running ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "outbound campaigns through Apollo.io",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", pipe those leads directly into Nutshell so nothing falls through the cracks.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The integration setup is straightforward, and most connections take under five minutes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "7. Review Reports Weekly, Not Quarterly",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Set a recurring calendar event every Monday: 15 minutes reviewing Nutshell's pipeline and activity reports. Look at deals that stalled, reps who need support, and sequences that are underperforming. This cadence keeps your team sharp and your forecasts accurate.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
