            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Nutshell CRM good for small teams?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell is built specifically for small to mid-size B2B teams. It's easy to set up, doesn't require a dedicated admin, and scales as your team grows. Most teams are fully operational within a day of signing up.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does Nutshell CRM cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nutshell offers straightforward pricing with plans starting at a competitive monthly rate per user. There are no hidden fees, and every plan includes core features like pipeline management, email sequences, and reporting. You can test everything with a 14-day free trial.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Nutshell CRM replace my email marketing tool?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
