        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, for many teams. Nutshell includes built-in email marketing features—drip campaigns, newsletters, and automated sequences—so you can manage outreach without a separate platform. It's one of the reasons Nutshell earned G2's Email Marketing Leader recognition.",
